  二、R#3.5 无关引用的处理（需要调整）

  你的回复：

  ▎ "these works focus on urban traffic flow prediction and cloud data center virtual machine allocation, which fall outside the scope of 3D point cloud analysis. Including them would not provide meaningful technical context for our work"

  这个回复过于生硬。你说"不在点云范围内，没意义"——审稿人可能会觉得你在说他的建议没意义。

  师兄在处理类似情况（R3要求加PETA数据集）时是这样说的：

  ▎ "Thanks for your nice advice. We provided experiments on the PETA dataset in Tab. 6 of the revised manuscript."

  他先说谢谢建议，然后直接告诉你在论文哪里补充了。从来不解释"为什么不接受"，而是用行动表示接受了。

  给你的建议：删掉解释"为什么不相关"那一整段。直接说：

  ▎ "We thank the reviewer for this suggestion. After careful consideration, we have instead added several recent point cloud references that more directly contextualize our contributions in Section 2, including [TBD references]. The suggested
  ▎ traffic flow and cloud computing references have not been included as they address different application domains."

  这样既拒绝了，又给了台阶，而且把话题引向了"我们加了什么"而非"我们为什么不加你给的"。

